{
  "stem": "3475.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I, I never met anybody from his side of the family, mostly-- only from my mother's side of the family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was a doll.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very soft-- very soft-hearted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could never go out by a beggar without giving him some money-- a very good-natured, soft-hearted person.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Both of them were, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother always had people at home that were worst off than we were, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would stay for a night or many nights.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she used to feed them-- a very charitable person, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember many times when we didn't have it, other relatives took care of us, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People would help each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started going-- I went to-- I think, at the age of 14, I went to this school called [POLISH], in Polish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a trade high school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- we had half, half a day of theory and a half a day of practice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a-- on a, a low level of machinist work, you know, mostly working by hand with files and hammers and drills and, and then, at the end, going to more an advanced machinist work, running all different-- you know, like lathes and mills and shapers, and machines of this kind, you know-- at the end.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I really didn't like it that much, to tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my father felt that I should have a trade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says-- he used to say a man-- a [NON-ENGLISH] in Jewish means a tradesman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH] will always make a living, he said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's why-- that was his influence on that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Europe, you didn't argue with your parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You did mostly what your parents asked you-- told you to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
